"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:41:03.000Z","msg":"叫停美韓軍事演習<br />\n變做美韓朝軍事演習<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f6bfa0d4eefd4862cdb59a16c1694eb5159ace","tid":699845,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:46:20.000Z","msg":"&quot;When the President of the United States announces unilaterally to the leader of North Korea that we are going to stop our military exercises with our allies, Japan and Korea, and does not first tell those allies ... and then goes on to say that someday he'd like to get our troops out of Asia,&quot; Green said, &quot;that's an astonishing development.&quot;<br />\n'It's inappropriate'<br />\nMany praised Trump for pursuing dialogue over confrontation. But Trump's move on military exercises reinforced concerns about his commitment to longstanding US alliances, particularly because he was offering a goal long sought by both Pyongyang and Beijing without consulting South Korea or Japan.<br />\nOthers said that in giving away a significant chip so early in the game, Trump was undermining his negotiators' leverage.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2018/06/12/politics/trump-north-korea-military-exercises/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-north-korea-military-exercises%2Findex.html&d=jLxFJ%2FU7YEb3387IAD0s0%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=a2745f8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-north-korea-military-exercises%2Findex.html&h=914fb610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/2018/06/12/politics/trump-north-korea-military-exercises/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"01e533ea59e4a53abf8fcc6d9f24a3d64b5d8a18","tid":699845,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46f6bfa0d4eefd4862cdb59a16c1694eb5159ace","tid":699845,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:46:20.000Z","msg":"&quot;When the President of the United States announces unilaterally to the leader of North Korea that we are going to stop our military exercises with our allies, Japan and Korea, and does not first tell those allies ... and then goes on to say that someday he'd like to get our troops out of Asia,&quot; Green said, &quot;that's an astonishing development.&quot;<br />\n'It's inappropriate'<br />\nMany praised Trump for pursuing dialogue over confrontation. But Trump's move on military exercises reinforced concerns about his commitment to longstanding US alliances, particularly because he was offering a goal long sought by both Pyongyang and Beijing without consulting South Korea or Japan.<br />\nOthers said that in giving away a significant chip so early in the game, Trump was undermining his negotiators' leverage.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2018/06/12/politics/trump-north-korea-military-exercises/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-north-korea-military-exercises%2Findex.html&d=jLxFJ%2FU7YEb3387IAD0s0%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=a2745f8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-north-korea-military-exercises%2Findex.html&h=914fb610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/2018/06/12/politics/trump-north-korea-military-exercises/index.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944714757ffb1f4e8c9f5218903f582496c61de1","tid":699845,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ccd3f84a3118f8d8990b841fd3281e35084fe2f","tid":699845,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:41:03.000Z","msg":"叫停美韓軍事演習<br />\n變做美韓朝軍事演習<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"